Encoding for special characters in java
UTF-8 handles all the special characters in written language.
Cient encoding needs to be done at both client and server side .
html page like 
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">

in server side in web.xml.and for get http method setting has to be done in tomcat . 

for more details see below link:
https://dertompson.com/2007/01/29/encoding-filter-for-java-web-applications/
